properties.areaDesc: Waters from Point Pinos to Point Piedras Blancas 10-60 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 8 at 2:24AM PST until January 9 at 9:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
seas 8 to 10 feet at 12 seconds expected.

* WHERE...Waters from Point Pinos to Point Piedras Blancas 10-
60 NM.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, until 3 AM PST early this
morning. For the Small Craft Advisory, from 3 AM to 9 PM PST
Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM PST EARLY THIS MORNING... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 AM TO 9 PM PST THURSDAY
